ch semester.  Meal Plans: Residents living in all buildings except MRH, PSR, SSR, and TBH are required to select a meal plan .        Academic and Residential Complex     Residents living in ARC are required to select a meal plan. The rate shown below includes the average Meal Plan price based on 15 meals per week. See 2019-2020 Meal Plan section below for details of 2019-2020 academic year offerings.  Contract Dates: All ARC contracts are for the entire academic year, including the following dates: August 20, 2020 - December 11, 2020 and January 10, 2021 - May 7, 2021.    Room Style  Room  Room and Meal Plan (Please see meal plans below)    Single  $11,309  $14,579    Double  $9,836  $13,106    Semi-Suite Single  $13,966  $17,236    Semi-Suite Double  $11,680  $14,950         Commons West (CMW)     Residents living in CMW are required to select a meal plan. The rate shown below includes the average Meal Plan price based on 15 meals per week. See 2019-2020 Meal Plan section below for details of 2019-2020 academic year offerings.  Contract Dates: All ARC contracts are for the entire academic year, including the following dates: August 20, 2020 - December 11, 2020 and January 10, 2021 - May 7, 2021.    Room Style  Room  Room and Meal Plan (please see meal plans below)      Single  $9,247  $12,517    Double  $8,263  $11,533    Triple  $7,520  $10,790         Courtyard (CTY)     Residents living in CTY are required to select a meal plan. The rate shown below includes the average Meal Plan price based on 15 meals per week. See 2019-2020 Meal Plan section below for details of 2019-2020 academic year offerings.  Contract Dates: All ARC contracts are for the entire academic year, including the following dates: August 20, 2020 - December 11, 2020 and January 10, 2021 - May 7, 2021.    Room Style  Room  Room and Meal Plan (please see meal plans below)      Cluster Single [3 Residents]  $10,226  $13,496    Cluster Single [5 Residents]  $9,853  $13,123    Cluster Single [7–9 Re